description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 30, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 90, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 3 for East, 8 for South, and 1 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [90 Votes, Common]
